author: wrowe
msg: On Darwin 9.0 the NSLoad... dyld API is deprecated; use dlopen.
On HPUX 64bit PA-RISC or IA64... shl_ API is deprecated; use dlopen.
(Unless we can't in which case we'll jump on shl at the end.)
Heck, we can even shortcircuit os2's detection phase, it's custom.
